# Output

This directory stores analysis outputs including tables and figures.

## Subdirectories

### tables/
Statistical tables, regression results, and t-test outputs in CSV format.

### figures/
Plots, visualizations, and diagnostic charts in PNG/PDF format.

## Generated By
- R scripts in Phase 3 (scripts 05-07)

## Notes
- Files in this directory are generated outputs
- Can be safely deleted and regenerated
- Add to .gitignore if outputs are large or frequently regenerated
